strings.Value: "Heh, I wish I could pore over the Technic League's notes... They've done so many experiments! They must have a trove of scientific data."

"Experiments? You should try the experiments I had to go through, you wouldn't hold up for an hour! But never mind. We'll meet those experimenters again. And I'm gonna rip them to pieces with my bare hands! Slo-o-o-wly!"
